Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.63,0:00:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機即將抵達射手座旋臂的維奧斯星系 進行Defold
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:09.81,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}開始超時空航行稱為Fold 結束航行稱為Defold
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子電離化水平良好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於在Defold時會伴有輕微震盪 請注意繫好安全帶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓派…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒一醒 雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們差不多快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是GFS-108 屬於Galaxy星際航線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frontier控制塔 請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GFS-108 這裡是Frontier控制塔 歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本船隊對『銀河妖精』雪露小姐的來訪表示衷心的歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海…

Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去曾經發生過一場人類與天頂星巨人之間的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:57.56,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1110,970)}Zentradi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類在首次與地球外生命的戰爭中 經歷了瀕於滅亡的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把未來寄托於向宇宙進發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去尋找新的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了向銀河各個方向的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 到了公元2059年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史上第25個移民船團Macross Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝著銀河的中心區域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續著「大航海」之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七瀨 不一起去Cranberry購物中心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 今天要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 盧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迴旋三周之後的急速反轉上升
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊 我來的話轉5圈也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是演唱會的餘興節目而已 那樣做風險太大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一如既往地自信啊 阿露特公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣的樣子也那麼美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的拿到雪露的票啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是為了蘭華
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說沒有什麼不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議(Deculture) 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有麻煩了 蘭華
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的天然豬肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷掉的話就太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有什麼不測的話就會成為國際問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必謹慎地處理好 格拉斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 總統閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到達人工重力區了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請留意腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看上去很疲勞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時差疲勞和Fold的暈眩 糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要取消採訪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古蕾絲 你忘了我是誰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪露·諾姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:27.18,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}銀河流行榜 連續17周蟬聯榜首記錄的保持者 銀河的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.91,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}來自Macross Galaxy船團的藝人 雪露·諾姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.44,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}在歷時三個月的銀河巡迴演出之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她來了 雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就能見到她了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她呼吸著同樣的空氣 真是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿露特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西北偏北的風 風速每秒4米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈射器連接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎良好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑翔翼良好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上風了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌舞伎登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空門 天空門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來點咖啡 果汁怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要遲到了 要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有更衣室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要對表演內容指手畫腳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是客戶的要求啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼「把高危險 花哨的動作給我去掉」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:07:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去掉阿露特前輩的高空螺旋也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別激動呀 盧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這種程度的工作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這是我作為隊長的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准反對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是一幅生氣的表情 絕世的美貌就糟蹋了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意見的話下次拿第一再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬年老二的阿露特公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米海爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實很想看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特前輩的高空螺旋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是兩千米高度就到頂的天空罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是飛 高度被定死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能駕駛Valkyrie就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是這種玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的Ex-gear和軍隊使用的也算是同一種規格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩畢業之後想參軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做民間飛行員的話不是也能飛行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規定好了的航線嗎 沒什麼興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想呆在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一個讓人窒息的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RE/8 請回答 RE/8
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快 要快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 全濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為去不成演唱會了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太漂亮了 還想是女孩子在換衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是女人!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無人戰機隊到達船隊前方的小行星地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20秒之後與目標相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有干擾?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了EPM電子干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迷路了 心想爬到樹上大概就知道怎麼走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和煙霧一樣往高處爬麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 過分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你幫我帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是你自己跟來的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 下次讓我來答謝你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在「娘娘」打工 要來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「娘娘」?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘娘 娘娘 你好喵
